<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ewr, unser und
                            <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> reichs stette <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
                        guten frewnde <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> marggraf <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                        Brandemburg nehst zu <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sein, also hat uns
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der marggraf von
                            <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        seid aber <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>desgleiche<ex>n</ex></expan> er <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<add>und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> stetten</add> auch
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> mag
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so
                                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wir zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> Barthlomes Neythart,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ratschreib<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir
                            <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, mit ew <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        reden. Und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                            <expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, was er zu disem mal
                        von <expan>sölich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir
                        im des <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und uns ewr
                            <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und guten
                            <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darinn beweisen wellet als etc. Das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Bartholomei.</ab>
